  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The upstream p2p discv5 package has several panics and unsafe slice access.\r\n\r\nWe should fork the code changes or write a new discv5 to change the API to be safer at runtime. \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/fjl/go-ethereum/tree/discover-v5-rebase/p2p\r\n\r\nExample panic that killed the testnet:\r\n```\r\npanic: runtime error: slice bounds out of range\r\n\r\ngoroutine 12088 [running]:\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/p2p/enode.splitNodeItemKey(0xc001fe2986, 0x7, 0x3d, 0xaeeeac7c345cdb61, 0x1c12ec867effb1db, 0x3bddc7511ad2647e, 0xd1f5326af3a951c1, 0xc001fe2983, 0x7, 0x3d, ...)\r\n        external/com_github_ethereum_go_ethereum/p2p/enode/nodedb.go:175 +0x1fb\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/p2p/enode.(*DB).expireNodes(0xc000803a00)\r\n        external/com_github_ethereum_go_ethereum/p2p/enode/nodedb.go:339 +0x1a0\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/p2p/enode.(*DB).expirer(0xc000803a00)\r\n        external/com_github_ethereum_go_ethereum/p2p/enode/nodedb.go:317 +0x84\r\ncreated by github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/p2p/enode.(*DB).ensureExpirer.func1\r\n        external/com_github_ethereum_go_ethereum/p2p/enode/nodedb.go:306 +0x3e\r\n```",
